entity.name: Labour set to announce new party leader

text:
It’s the honour and privilege of my life to be elected as Leader of the Labour Party. 

I will lead this great party into a new era, with confidence and hope, so that when the time comes, we can serve our country again – in government. https://t.co/F4X088FTYY
